{"tid":1739241,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"馬拉樓有窿味","createTime":"2019-11-19T13:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T19:17:09.000Z","uid":149342,"like":23,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7b160f238e41f486c393e97415cb6a6a99f14aac","tid":1739241,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:48:50.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇過啲馬拉樓片，近排突然發現郭釗出片講坊間賣馬拉樓ge 係 markup 盤,<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GN9BQnf6eB4&amp;lc=Ugw98dpCpj4RJTnWVJx4AaABAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGN9BQnf6eB4%26lc%3DUgw98dpCpj4RJTnWVJx4AaABAg&d=UXFjm%2BDMXm%2Fj1yL9MgXeqGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=e09bcb61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GN9BQnf6eB4&amp;lc=Ugw98dpCpj4RJTnWVJx4AaABAg</a><br />\n<br />\n咁睇嘅情勢，應該馬拉樓都差唔多玩完.<br />\n點解咁講呢，通常一條水如果係夠大嘅，即係你有你做，我有我做，大家都有肉食嘅，咁基本上各有各做，就唔需要篤爆同行嘅.但當條水越嚟越窄,咁就開始要互咬啦.<br />\n簡單講，如果大馬樓源源不絕有水魚上,咁大家只係target自己啲客咁就OK，但如果你發覺越嚟越難搞嘅時候，你就可能寧願篤爆個game，咁樣反而幫自己贏得一個專家嘅美名,博最後啲水魚會搵自己，但咁樣一搞就等於減價戰一樣，屍橫遍野血流成河"},{"pid":"1f393c8d3c6c74cc8f4cf9722433543983355f86","tid":1739241,"uid":94538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"[1120和你塞] 想熱門有多啲和你塞既post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739192\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739192</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4a8e3287e40661260be9ae8d09cd4e89dfe5821","tid":1739241,"uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:02:20.000Z","msg":"傻嘅先買。<br />\n<br />\n有錢買823唔好？"},{"pid":"c3f52e859ede2cd1b43bc164c0bef7843800d754","tid":1739241,"uid":51183,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"諗起森林城市<br />\n有期好多C9比人水左買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0dbd8acb6ab8bf3918611de030e99402cbe28a3","tid":1739241,"uid":14690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T14:08:17.000Z","msg":"曼